        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3866/173230/3866_173230_000059_000022.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3866",
        "content": "But he has even used me more cruelly still; he persists in suspecting me; it is he who is having me watched.",
