        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3866/9920/3866_9920_000001_000015.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3866",
        "content": "\"Thirty francs.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3866_9920_000001_000016",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3866/9920/3866_9920_000001_000016.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3866",
        "content": "\"What is your name?\" \"Olympie.\" \"You shall have fifty francs, and you shall be called Nicolette.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3866_9920_000003_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3866/9920/3866_9920_000003_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3866",
        "content": "He had all sorts of prejudices and took all sorts of liberties.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3866_9920_000003_000013",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3866/9920/3866_9920_000003_000013.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3866",
        "content": "You are finely taken aback, and really, you are excessively ignorant.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3866_9920_000003_000020",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3866/9920/3866_9920_000003_000020.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3866",
        "content": "This manner of procedure was good tempered.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3866_9920_000003_000025",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3866/9920/3866_9920_000003_000025.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3866",
        "content": "He added: \"I insist upon it that the mother shall treat them well. I shall go to see them from time to time.\" And this he did.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3866_9920_000003_000039",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3866/9920/3866_9920_000003_000039.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3866",
        "content": "He took an immense amount of snuff, and had a particularly graceful manner of plucking at his lace ruffle with the back of one hand.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3866_9920_000008_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3866/9920/3866_9920_000008_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3866",
        "content": "He dined at five o'clock, and after that his door was open.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3866_9920_000010_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3866/9920/3866_9920_000010_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3866",
        "content": "They had come into the world ten years apart.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3866_9920_000011_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3866/9920/3866_9920_000011_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3866",
        "content": "No paradise becomes terrestrial in our day.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3866_9920_000011_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3866/9920/3866_9920_000011_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3866",
        "content": "The younger wedded the man of her dreams, but she died.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3866_9920_000013_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3866/9920/3866_9920_000013_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3866",
        "content": "Her modesty was carried to the other extreme of blackness. She cherished a frightful memory of her life; one day, a man had beheld her garter.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3866_9920_000014_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3866/9920/3866_9920_000014_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3866",
        "content": "Age had only served to accentuate this pitiless modesty.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3866_9920_000016_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3866/9920/3866_9920_000016_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3866",
        "content": "In spite of this favored Lancer, the label: Prude, under which we have classed her, suited her to absolute perfection.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3866_9920_000018_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3866/9920/3866_9920_000018_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3866",
        "content": "Mademoiselle Vaubois, perfect in her style, was the ermine of stupidity without a single spot of intelligence.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3866_9920_000019_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3866/9920/3866_9920_000019_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3866",
        "content": "This is the case with passive natures.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3866_9920_000019_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3866/9920/3866_9920_000019_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3866",
        "content": "There breathed from her whole person the stupor of a life that was finished, and which had never had a beginning.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3866_9920_000022_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3866/9920/3866_9920_000022_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3866",
        "content": "This was his grandson.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    }
]